---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="My Approach - Mary Gansallo" description="How I design AI products: systems thinking, intelligent UX, prototyping, and deep collaboration with engineering.">
  <div class="page-shell">
    <article class="approach-card card">
      <h1>My Approach</h1>

      <p>
        I design AI products by understanding systems before screens, validating ideas early through prototypes, and partnering closely with engineering. My work sits at the intersection of product strategy, AI interaction design, and enterprise UX.
      </p>

      <hr />

      <h2>🧠 Understand the System</h2>
      <p>
        Great products start with understanding how everything connects—not just the interface.
      </p>
      <p>
        I map relationships between users, permissions, data, business goals, and technical constraints before designing experiences.
      </p>
      <p><strong>Focus</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Product strategy</li>
        <li>Customer research</li>
        <li>Information architecture</li>
        <li>Systems mapping</li>
      </ul>

      <hr />

      <h2>🤖 Design Human–AI Collaboration</h2>
      <p>
        AI should make people more capable—not less informed.
      </p>
      <p>
        I design agentic experiences that explain their reasoning, recommend actions, and keep people in control through transparency and review.
      </p>
      <p><strong>Deliverables</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>AI workflows</li>
        <li>Agent experiences</li>
        <li>Trust patterns</li>
        <li>Decision flows</li>
      </ul>

      <hr />

      <h2>⚡ Prototype with Code</h2>
      <p>
        Working software answers questions faster than static mockups.
      </p>
      <p>
        I build high-fidelity prototypes and collaborate with engineering early to validate ideas, reduce implementation risk, and accelerate delivery.
      </p>
      <p><strong>Tools</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Figma</li>
        <li>Claude Code</li>
        <li>VS Code Copilot</li>
        <li>React</li>
        <li>Storybook</li>
        <li>MCP</li>
      </ul>

      <hr />

      <div class="tools-inline">
        <h2>Tools I Reach For</h2>
        <p class="tools-subtitle">A snapshot of the stack I use across product, design, engineering, and AI work.</p>
        <div class="tools-table-wrap">
          <table class="tools-table" aria-label="Tools I Reach For">
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th scope="col">Product</th>
                <th scope="col">Design</th>
                <th scope="col">Engineering</th>
                <th scope="col">AI</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td>Figma</td>
                <td>FigJam</td>
                <td>React</td>
                <td>Claude</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>VS Code</td>
                <td>Storybook</td>
                <td>TypeScript</td>
                <td>GitHub Copilot</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Azure DevOps</td>
                <td>Miro</td>
                <td>MCP</td>
                <td>ChatGPT</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .approach-card {
    max-width: 920px;
    margin: 10px auto 30px;
    padding: 36px;
  }

  .approach-card h1 {
    font-size: 42px;
    margin: 0 0 14px;
  }

  .approach-card h2 {
    font-size: 30px;
    margin: 28px 0 10px;
  }

  .approach-card h3 {
    font-size: 24px;
    margin: 22px 0 8px;
  }

  .approach-card p {
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0 0 14px;
    font-size: 18px;
  }

  .approach-card ul {
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    padding-left: 24px;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-size: 18px;
  }

  .approach-card li {
    margin: 0 0 6px;
  }

  .approach-card hr {
    border: 0;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
    margin: 24px 0;
  }

  .tools-inline h2 {
    font-size: 34px;
    margin: 0 0 10px;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .tools-subtitle {
    margin: 0 0 22px;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .tools-table-wrap {
    overflow-x: auto;
  }

  .tools-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.14);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.14);
  }

  .tools-table th,
  .tools-table td {
    text-align: left;
    padding: 16px 0;
    font-size: 20px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .tools-table th {
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .tools-table tbody tr:last-child td {
    border-bottom: 0;
  }

  .tools-table th:not(:last-child),
  .tools-table td:not(:last-child) {
    padding-right: 20px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .approach-card {
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .approach-card h1 {
      font-size: 34px;
    }

    .approach-card h2 {
      font-size: 26px;
    }

    .tools-inline h2 {
      font-size: 30px;
    }

    .tools-table th,
    .tools-table td {
      font-size: 18px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .tools-table {
      min-width: 640px;
    }

    .tools-table th,
    .tools-table td {
      padding: 14px 0;
    }
  }
</style>
